comments: Harris (BKN) legally contests Lowry's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
Harden (BKN) briefly engages with Powell (TOR) after Powell tips the ball and makes marginal contact with Powell's arm prior to Powell securing the rebound.
Powell (TOR) tips the ball and makes marginal contact with Irving (BKN) as they engage during the rebound.
Irving (BKN) legally contests VanVleet's (TOR) jump shot attempt.

Harden (BKN) draws Powell (TOR) into the air and as Powell returns to the floor he does not make contact with Harden until after the release of his jump shot. The contact is marginal and does not affect the jump shot attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) takes more than two steps after he has gathered the ball and before he releases the pass.
Siakam (TOR) legally contests Shamet's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Irving (BKN) during the rebound.
Harris (BKN) makes contact with Lowry's (TOR) body that affects his SQBR during his dribble.
Green (BKN) makes marginal contact with Siakam's (TOR) arm during his shot attempt at the basket.
After the release of Harden's (BKN) shot attempt, VanVleet (TOR) makes marginal contact with Harden as he returns to the floor following his driving shot attempt.
As Harden (BKN) slips the defender, Siakam (TOR) jumps vertically during the driving shot attempt.
Harden (BKN) cleanly deflects the ball away from Powell (TOR) and any arm contact that occurs is marginal.
Siakam (TOR) and Harris (BKN) make marginal contact with each other as they engage and disengage during the loose ball.
Lowry (TOR) dives on top of Harris (BKN) and impedes his ability to move during the loose ball.
Harris (BKN) makes marginal contact with Lowry's (TOR) arm on the gather prior to Lowry successfully completing the pass.
VanVleet (TOR) briefly engages and disengages with Harris (BKN) during the screen.
Harris (BKN) commits a take foul on Siakam (TOR).
Powell (TOR) legally contests Irving's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) initially clamps Harris's (BKN) arm during the rebound, but he releases and does not restrict his ability to get to the rebound.
